textBeforeTable: Music Read the full recap Recap Cameron Hicks is working at a grocery store when he gets a text message with an address. A high-pitched tone plays in the background. A woman asks him for directions and then casually says that it’s time to kill. Cameron goes into the back and his boss makes casual conversation, and then says that it’s time to kill and Cameron should pull the trigger...
